        "created_at": "2025-11-12T22:04:33.237Z",
        "cooked": "<p>For anyone who’s interested: We found a semi usable workaround, using OBS Studio. You can create a virtual camera of your Desktop and enable the camera in Signal to get pseudo bidirectional screensharing working.</p>\n<p>Sadly though apparently Signal’s video compression, makes text a little blurry.</p>",
